these are just some things i need to say to people...

Frankee!!- im not mad at u..i love u and i want to be best friends again. its just that u really hurt my feelings and pissed me off when you told andrea that. but it is cool. everyone messess up, and i love u soooo much!

Cameron- i know that was u on the prank call..im not that stupid. And PLEASE...LEO? yea, right..

Sophia!!- i will see u soon this weekend! can't wait for the big party! but why are we going to swim in the Winter at night? im not getting that but OK

Lexa!!- i miss you sooo much! how is new york? ur not going to leave me out here alone, are u??? i miss u...

Jordan!- hey hottie..i miss ur black ass! come back to LA! fuck North Carolina!

Yelena!!- i have never had so much fun with anyone! u are so funny, and light hearted...oh yeah- can u help me with math? i dont get it..

Sarah- my 7th grade buddy!! ur sooo cool, i love u...all of those lLLLLLOOOONNNNGGGGGGGgg walks to El Poll Loco and Carls Jr....mmmm...carls....el pollo.....loco..mmm

Danny- that was so funny yesterday! omg..u totally fell head first into the horse shit! omg. lolol

Chris- welll...if u cant get a girl...u can certainly get my basketball run over by a Porsche Speedster..lol, i cnat beleive it didnt pop!!

Arash- what the hell is going on? i dont get it... what happened on friday?

Jessica!!!!- what the hell is going on with our classes?!?!?!?? what the fuck? senority rules, and we shoudl be in fucking yearbook.....DAMNIT!


well..i feel better...OH YEAH!! the quote of the day is: "Life is not about counting the breaths you take, but about counting the moments that take your breaht away."
                                                        much love
                                                           -Blue 15

yeah, yeah, i know...my layout sucks! not that i have a layout anyways..but whatever..

anyways, omg! i hate school...i mean, it is cool to see our friends and stuff, but COME ON! i miss summer so bad...I hate my classes! im in like all 7th grade classes..atleast ill be the "big dog" lol..not really. 

gotta go do fuckin homework..aghghgh..oh yeah! the quote for today is, "A player that makes a team great is better than a great player"

                                              much love and good luck!
                                                      -blue 15

ughhh, tomorrow is our last day and i am so fucking BUMBed (i hope that is how u spell it..haha)
Frankee is over, so i can't write long..but the quote for today is....ummm..."always play to win, never play not to lose" i guess this quote or saying or whatever it is, is a little hard to get and weird until u kind of understand it..

well, thanks and ill see everybody on thursday..peace out
                                                     blue 15

summer is coming to an end. :( only 2 days till school! I'm happy, but not at the same time. I hope i get some good teachers, and have good classes. This year, I am going to do things a lot differently. For all of the people who I maybe didnt get along with last year or whatever, I just wanted to say sorry, and i hope that we can start over this year. A lot of times, my words were twisted, and people lied, but maybe if i wasnt such a bitch, that wouldn't happen. So, I am sorry. 

anyways...today was really fun. In the morning i had to go running and do my "training workout" (that is what my dad calls it, lol) then I went to the park to shoot around a littl bit. After that, my dad and I went and bought some heavier weights for training. Then, we ate at La Salsa..mmmmm, after that, we went to Gelsons to load up on stuff that we already have, lol. then, we went back home. We hung out for a little bit, but then my dad decided to go to the beach. I stayed home and waited for Frankee (who is like one of my best friends EVER lol) to pick me up to go to her niece's party. OMG, it was SOOOO much fun..now that I am back home, I am bored out of my mind..lol

I know that this is kind of different, but after all of my journal entries, i am going to leave a quote...today's quote is: "If you don't use it, you lose it."

                                     Thanks for reading, and PLEASE COMMENT!

                                                            -blue 15
